⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of The Tarnished
node ER · ER · ⟦The Tarnished:ER:e3c90c⟧

WHO   — The Tarnished — the graceless exile called back to the Ring
WHAT  — The player's role — a descendant of Godfrey's exiled warriors, long stripped of the Erdtree's grace, recalled to the Lands Between after the Shattering.
WHERE — ER · Elden Ring  Framework inputs: the cast  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — The Order broken by the Shattering can only be repaired or replaced by one who stands outside it — the Tarnished may end as Elden Lord of any of several ages, or as Lord of Frenzied Flame.
HOW   — Undying as long as grace holds, climbing from nobody to slayer of demigods, guided by the grace that now leads the graceless to the Ring.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  Grace abandoned them first; now grace calls the graceless home to break or mend the Ring.

